<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Some very usefull enhancements for Zend_Db.</p>

<p>Zend_Db functionality for working with table structure.</p>

<p>Possible interface:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$table = new Table(); // extends Zend_Db_Table

$table-&gt;deleteField(
    title // field title in DB
);

$table-&gt;addField(
    title, // field title in DB
    'VARCHAR', //type
    255, // length
    null, // default value
    ...
);

$table-&gt;alterField(
    title, // field title in DB
    'VARCHAR', //type
    255, // length
    null, // default value
    ...
);
</code></pre>

<p>Functionality for table structure import into DB and export to xml or other format would be very usefull too.</p>

<p>Possible interface:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$table = new Table(); // extends Zend_Db_Table

$table-&gt;importStructure('table_structure.xml');

$table-&gt;exportStructure('table_structure.xml');

</code></pre>

